<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Cyrus Kingsbury</author>
<hymn_number>139</hymn_number>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Joy for the Gospel ƲIT139</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yakoke, Chisʋs ma!
 Chishno pulla kak osh
 Yakni holitopa hina
 Ish pim atahli tok.

[V2]
 Yakoke, pi yukpa;
 Chim okla pia hʋt
 Ʋba nitak ai a̱hli ya̱
 Ont pisa pi bʋnna.

[V3]
 Yakoke, Chisʋs ma!
 Yakni paknaka ma,
 Mi̱ko tʋnʋp pehlichi a̱
 Ish im aiyachi tok.

[V4]
 Chisʋs okcha̱ya ma!
 Nana ai a̱hli kʋt
 A mahli ushta kanima
 A minti kʋt iksho.

[V5]
 Ʋba holitopa
 I̱ mi̱ko Chisʋs ma!
 Chu̱kʋsh achukma pi bʋnna
 E chim asilhhʋshke.

[V6]
 Ayukpa a̱hli kʋt
 Yakni 'lʋppa iksho,
 Ithʋnʋt pin taiyaha tok;
 Ish pi apelashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Yakoke, Chisʋs ma!</aka>
</song>